Title: RoboKreta
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: CERN/3.0 Date: Monday, 06-Jan-97 21:29:54 GMT Content-Type: text/html Content-Length: 804 Last-Modified: Sunday, 21-Jul-96 15:05:00 GMT RoboKreta RoboKreta RoboKreta-Besar RoboKreta-Kicik RoboKreta-Besar and RoboKreta-Kicik are two autonomous intelligent toy cars built using the chassis and motors of two fast radio-controlled (RC) toy racing cars.
